Name: Trafic Road Rush
About the game: Do you like speed and cars? Then Trafic Road Rush is made for you. Feel the speed and drive on an endless track with multiple racing modes. Earn points and buy new cool cars to be the fastest. Realistic 3D graphics. Several game modes. Buying wheelbarrows and crazy speed. Use WASD or Arrow buttons for car control
